name: CMFallDetectionEvent.UserResolution
desc: User resolutions for fall detection events.

items.name: case dismissed
items.desc: The user dismissed the fall event alert, but didn’t explicitly confirm or reject the event.

items.name: case rejected
items.desc: The user rejected the fall event.

items.name: case unresponsive
items.desc: The user didn’t respond to the fall event and the system hasn’t detected recovery motions.
